The paper discusses the challenge of increasing the explainability of Cyber-Physical Systems (CPS) and their engineering tools, which requires interdisciplinary research from multiple fields such as software engineering, systems engineering, and related fields. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SE (Software Engineering), followed by cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
